OL,7,FITV News Meridian's Megan Samrai
OL,8,Freports on the veterans taking on a
OL,9,Fnew challenge
OL,11,FTwo Gurkha veterans, and lifelong
OL,12,Ffriends, who were injured in battle
OL,13,Fjust one day apart are cycling from
OL,14,FKent to Belgium.
OL,16,FThey're raising money for the Royal
OL,17,FBritish Legion Industries, which
OL,18,Fprovides financial, social and
OL,19,Femotional support to members and
OL,20,Fveterans of the British Armed Forces,
OL,21,Ftheir families and dependants.
