OL,7,FAs childhood friends, Vinod Budhathoki
OL,8,Fand Tirthraj Thapa both grew up in
OL,9,FNepal before serving in the Royal
OL,10,FGurkha Rifles.
OL,12,FWhilst stationed in Afghanistan, both
OL,13,Fwere hurt by improvised explosive
OL,14,Fdevices, with Vinod losing both legs
OL,15,Fand Tirthraj losing his leg below the
OL,16,Fknee.
OL,18,FLife-changing surgery has resulted in
OL,19,Fhim having to wear a prosthetic limb
OL,20,Fbut Thirthraj has rebuilt his life
OL,21,Fsince being wounded in 2010.
