OL,7,FTirthraj now a team leader at the
OL,8,FRBLI's factory in Aylesford which
OL,9,Fspecialises in making road signs.
OL,11,FTirthraj said the injury first created
OL,12,Fhurdles which he's now been able to
OL,13,Fovercome. He said,
OL,15,F"At the beginning. It was very, very
OL,16,Fchallenging for me because I never had
OL,17,Fthat experience before. I was very
OL,18,Ffrustrated and I felt like I had no
OL,19,Ffuture for me.
