OL,7,F'But soon I realised that because of
OL,8,Fthe prosthetic, I can walk, I can do
OL,9,Flots of other things like cycling,
OL,10,Fplay golf. So it is an absolutely and
OL,11,Fbrilliant thing for me that changed my
OL,12,Flife."
OL,14,FThe 173km journey will end at Ypres in
OL,15,FBelgium, at the Menin Gate memorial
OL,16,Fwhich pays tribute to soldiers lost in
OL,17,Fthe first and second world war.
