OL,7,FIt's Tirthraj's fifth time embarking
OL,8,Fon the the cycle route to the Menin
OL,9,FGate and Vinod's first, who will use a
OL,10,Fhand bike.
OL,12,FBoth hoping to collect enough
OL,13,Fdonations to make a difference to the
OL,14,Flives of others.
OL,16,FPaula Ray from the RBLI said, "It's an
OL,17,Famazing events and the money raised
OL,18,Fgoes a long way to helping the village
OL,19,Fat Royal British Legion Industries.
